00:10:32.030 --> 00:10:32.870
Ouais.

00:10:33.510 --> 00:10:34.350
Président Wang,

00:10:34.510 --> 00:10:36.150
Tu as meilleure mine ces derniers temps.

00:10:37.330 --> 00:10:38.390
Merci.

00:10:40.510 --> 00:10:41.360
Cheng,

00:10:41.470 --> 00:10:43.270
